SUMMARY:Education Day with the Durham Bulls
DESCRIPTION:Get your tickets now — we’ll be on the concourse at the first Durham Bulls Education Day of 2026! Bulls Education Days are an opportunity for local students and teachers to enjoy offsite learning and have tons of fun while doing it. Stop by our information booth to learn about APS community programs and how you can foster or adopt our animals or volunteer at the shelter! Can’t wait to see you there!
URL:https://www.apsofdurham.org/event/education-day-with-the-durham-bulls/
LOCATION:Durham Bulls Athletic Park\, 409 Blackwell St\, Durham\, NC\, 27701
CATEGORIES:Education
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.apsofdurham.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/0414-Durham-Bulls-Education-Game-1.jpg
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:Animal Protection Society of Durham
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260418T130000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260418T170000
DTSTAMP:20260411T231230
CREATED:20260401T210921Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260401T210921Z
UID:165058-1776517200-1776531600@www.apsofdurham.org
SUMMARY:Out & About at the Scrap Exchange
DESCRIPTION:At the Scrap Exchange\, every day is Earth Day! That’s also the name of one of their biggest community gatherings of the year\, and we’re thrilled to be joining them again! We’ll have a few adoptable dogs in tow for you to hang out with and get to know better. They’re the stars of every event they attend\, of course\, but Everyday is Earth Day has tons of other fun in store too — music\, vendors\, a huge fill-a-box sale\, and much more! Come say happy 35th birthday to them\, and don’t forget to have your photo taken with Mongo!
URL:https://www.apsofdurham.org/event/out-about-at-the-scrap-exchange/
LOCATION:The Scrap Exchange\, 2050 Chapel Hill Rd.\, Durham\, NC\, 27707
CATEGORIES:Adoption Events
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.apsofdurham.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/0418-Scrap-Exchange.jpg
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:Animal Protection Society of Durham
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260425T110000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260425T150000
DTSTAMP:20260411T231230
CREATED:20260402T135725Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260402T135725Z
UID:165064-1777114800-1777129200@www.apsofdurham.org
SUMMARY:Canine Field Day
DESCRIPTION:Join us as we head to Durham Park & Rec’s Canine Field Day with a few adoptable dogs for you to meet\, greet\, and fall in love with! And if you’ve been meaning to get involved with APS\, our amazing volunteers will be on hand to tell you all about it. You and your own canine pal(s) can participate in fun field games and activities\, and we’ll take ours for a spin too! Field games will include an agility course\, non-competitive Frisbee catch & ball fetch area\, bobbing for treats\, a treasure hunt\, and so much more! And when your pup is tuckered out from the fun\, check out the pet market or grab a bite to eat at the food trucks!
URL:https://www.apsofdurham.org/event/canine-field-day-3/
LOCATION:Rock Quarry Park\, 701 Stadium Drive\, Durham\, NC\, 27701\, United States
CATEGORIES:Adoption Events,Education
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.apsofdurham.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/0425-Canine-Field-Day-with-DPR.jpg
END:VEVENT
