SUMMARY:Bark at the Park with Research Triangle High School
DESCRIPTION:We’ll be cheering on the RTHS Raptors girls’ soccer team with a few adoptable dogs as they take on East Wake Academy! RTHS will also be holding a raffle\, with a portion of the proceeds donated to APS. We’re so grateful for their donation — it helps us continue our lifesaving work! Come on out to root for the team\, meet some pups\, and support a cause you care about. See you there!
URL:https://www.apsofdurham.org/event/bark-at-the-park-with-research-triangle-high-school/
LOCATION:Mills Park\, 425 Mills Park Dr\, Cary\, NC\, 27519
CATEGORIES:Adoption Events,Fundraisers
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.apsofdurham.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/0429-Bark-at-the-Park-with-Research-Triangle-HS.jpg
END:VEVENT
