LAST-MODIFIED:20260313T190031Z
UID:164293-1780131600-1780144200@www.apsofdurham.org
SUMMARY:2026 Walk for the Animals!
DESCRIPTION:We hope you’ll join us for our biggest and best community event of the year! Registration is OPEN! Our Walk for the Animals brings together hundreds of animal lovers from all over the Triangle\, and the easy 1.5-mile walk around Duke’s East Campus is just one part of a fun-filled day for all ages! Have a laugh at our many pet contests\, run your pup through her paces on our mini-agility course\, and browse all kinds of goodies at our vendor fair. Join up with friends\, neighbors\, or colleagues to see who can raise the most money for the animals of APS! We couldn’t do what we do without your support — THANK YOU!
URL:https://www.apsofdurham.org/event/2026-walk-for-the-animals/
LOCATION:Duke University East Campus\, 712 Broad Street\, Durham\, 27705\, United States
CATEGORIES:Fundraisers
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.apsofdurham.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/16-9-ratio-Events-page_SMALLER.jpg
END:VEVENT
